AWS EC2 Migration Simulation: AMI Creation & Storage Lifecycle Demonstration
📋 Project Overview

This project simulates a real-world cloud migration by creating a reusable Amazon Machine Image (AMI) from a customized EC2 instance and launching a new instance from that image. It demonstrates infrastructure consistency, migration efficiency, and cost optimization through automated storage lifecycle policies.

Core Skills Demonstrated:

    EC2 instance configuration and customization

    AMI creation for infrastructure replication

    Storage lifecycle management with Data Lifecycle Manager (DLM)

    Cost optimization through tiered storage strategies

    Infrastructure as Code principles

