💰 Cost Optimization Summary
Strategy	Implementation	Cost Impact
AMI Deregistration	Remove unused AMIs after migration	Eliminates storage costs for inactive images
Snapshot Lifecycle	Auto-delete snapshots after 90 days	Prevents orphaned snapshot accumulation
Storage Tiering	Transition S3 data to IA/Glacier	Reduces storage costs by 50-80% for aged data
Right-sizing	Use t2.micro for demo workloads	Minimizes compute costs during testing
Auto-cleanup	DLM policies for automatic deletion	Eliminates human forgetfulness costs
