🛠️ Troubleshooting Guide
Issue	Likely Cause	Solution
systemctl commands fail	Connected via browser-based console instead of SSH	Use SSH with key pair as shown in Step 1.2
Unit httpd.service not found	Apache not installed	Run sudo dnf install -y httpd
Can't connect via browser	Security group missing HTTP rule	Add inbound rule: HTTP, port 80, source 0.0.0.0/0
AMI creation stuck	Instance in unstable state	Reboot source instance and retry
DLM policy not triggering	Missing tags on target resources	Verify snapshots have correct tags (MigrationPhase=Source-Image)
Data volume not mounting	Device name different	Run lsblk to identify correct device name
